        <div class="portfolio-col col-5">
          <p>
            As a programmer, I strive to create clean, readable, and
            maintainable code that can be reused in multiple projects. As a
            member of a team, I strive to create a safe, respectful, and fun
            environment where all members can express their opinion and ideas,
            leading to creative solutions that would have otherwise not been
            voiced. I have a passion for role-playing games and creating
            stories. I combined that passion with my skills as a programmer to
            create a website that documents the stories we create. Using
            WordPress, jQuery, custom fields, and other technologies, I can
            create a dynamic website that is easy to manage and creates an even
            more immersive environment that allows creativity to flourish.
          </p>
